openFile

  • openFile(file, fileType, openOptions?): Promise<any>

  • Open data file.

    Parameters

    • file: string | Blob | URL

      The data file.

    • fileType: FileType

      The type of the imported data file.

    • Optional openOptions: XlsxOpenOptions | SSJsonOpenOptions | CsvOpenOptions | SjsOpenOptions

      The options for imported data file.

    Returns Promise<any>

    Example

    viewer.openFile("Documents/HelloWorld.xlsx", FileType.XLSX, {loadHiddenSheets: true});
